// Canonical PUBLIC team-identity registry for the Kibana repo.
//
// This is the single source of truth for team *identity* (id, name, area,
// GitHub team/label, responsibilities). It is consumed by @kbn/code-owners
// (see src/teams.ts) and by external tooling.
//
// DO NOT add private operational data here (Slack channels, PagerDuty/oncall
// rotations, notification preferences). Those live in a private overlay repo
// and are joined to this registry by team "id".
//
// Each entry: { id, name, areas?, description?, github: { team?, label? }, responsibilities? }
// "areas" entries must each be one of @kbn/code-owners CODE_OWNER_AREAS.
